  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat, about 375°F (190°C).",
    "Thread shrimp, pineapple, and cilantro onto skewers, leaving some space between each piece.",
    "Mix harissa, lime juice, garlic, black pepper, and smoked paprika in a small bowl.",
    "Brush coconut oil onto both sides of the shrimp.",
    "Place the skewers on the grill and cook for 8-10 minutes, flipping halfway through.",
    "Remove from heat and brush with fish sauce.",
    "Let the skewers rest for 2 minutes before serving."
  ],
